snippet.title: Elementallis Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Elementallis on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1304280/Elementallis/

Join our community on Discord https://discord.com/invite/PCYHASD

Elementallis is a classic top down adventure with a modernized retro aesthetic. Explore a vast world and conquer the dungeons to obtain all the Elements and use them to solve puzzles and defeat your foes.

Trailer music by Raúl Sangonzalo https://soundcloud.com/raul-sangonzalo
Music Based Off Original Main Theme By Nicole Marie  T https://nicolemakesmusic.wixsite.com/nicolemariet
https://twitter.com/musicvsartstuff
https://www.youtube.com/c/nicolesproducerpack

Links of interest:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/elementallis
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Elementallis/
Website: http://elementallis.com
